  "original_title": "\u0b85\u0bb2\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bb2\u0b95 \u0bb0\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bc7\u0bb5\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0bae\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Limitation of office train services",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "Due to this, the Railway Department has announced that only 28 trains out of 48 office buses will be in service.",
        "Due to the demonstration by the department employees demanding fuel yesterday, the office train services that were scheduled to take place yesterday evening were also affected.",
        "Alleging that the railway department is improperly distributing fuel to the servicemen, some of the railway transport workers have gone on strike since yesterday afternoon."
      ],
